%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-day%20protest%2C%20which%20began%20on%20Sunday%2C%20sought%20to%20underline%20the%20%E2%80%9Clingering%20acute%20agrarian%20crisis%20and%20the%20resultant%20rural%20to%20urban%20migration%20of%20the%20pauperised%20peasantry%20and%20rural%20worker%20masses%E2%80%9D.%20A%20call%20was%20issued%20for%20%E2%80%9Cworker-farmer%20unity%20to%20challenge%20corporate-%20communal%20nexus%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20final%20day%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20protestors%20would%20march%20to%20Raj%20Bhavans%20to%20submit%20a%20charter%20of%20demands%20to%20the%20governors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20neoliberal%20policies%20are%20the%20genesis%20of%20the%20agrarian%20crisis.%20Its%20disastrous%20impacts%20spoil%20the%20lives%20of%20not%20only%20the%20peasantry%20but%20workers%20and%20youth%20too.%20The%20large-scale%20migration%20causes%20conducive%20environment%20for%20unbridled%20unemployment%2C%20large-scale%20privatisation%20of%20public%20service%20units%20(PSUs)%2C%20contractualisation%20and%20denial%20of%20basic%20rights%20of%20workers%20such%20as%20minimum%20wage%2C%20employment%20security%2C%20statutory%20old%20age%20pension%2C%20right%20to%20form%20association%2C%20collective%20bargaining%20and%20the%20right%20to%20strike.%20Thus%20eliminating%20the%20agrarian%20crisis%20has%20become%20the%20joint%20responsibility%20of%20the%20farmers%20as%20well%20as%20the%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20press%20statement%20released%20by%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%2C%20which%20is%20organising%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP-led%20Modi%20government%20is%20unleashing%20a%20brutal%20attack%20on%20the%20lives%20and%20livelihoods%20of%20the%20workers%20and%20farmers%20to%20facilitate%20corporate%20exploitation%20and%20profiteering.%20Also%2C%20the%20BJP-%20RSS%20combine%20is%20relying%20on%20communal%20politics%20bas