0taxes%20to%20fix%20the%20property%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20program%20in%20West%20Virginia%20is%20offering%20potential%20new%20residents%20%2412%2C000%20in%20cash.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221326%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22morgantown%20west%20virginia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60805f63c36a8a00185c6355%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22995%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20couple%20walks%20in%20downtown%20Morgantown%2C%20West%20Virginia.%3Cp%3EWest%20Virginia%20Tourism%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20Virginia%20launched%20a%20program%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fascendwv.com%2F%5C%22%3EAscend%20WV%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20attract%20out-of-state%20remote%20workers%20to%20Morgantown.%20To%20be%20eligible%2C%20potential%20residents%20must%20be%2018%20years%20or%20older%2C%20able%20to%20verify%20remote%20employment%2C%20and%20willing%20to%20move%20to%20the%20city%20of%2030%2C000%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20accepted%20to%20the%20program%20are%20expected%20to%20relocate%20to%20Morgantown%20%E2%80%94%20a%20vibrant%20college%20town%20home%20to%20West%20Virginia%20University%20%E2%80%94%20within%20six%20months%20to%20receive%20%2410%2C000%20in%20cash%20paid%20out%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20year.%20Another%20%242%2C000%20is%20to%20be%20paid%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20year.%20Other%20perks%20of%20the%20program%20include%20a%20coworking-space%20membership%20and%20free%20outdoor-gear%20rentals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fall%20of%202021%2C%20the%20program%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwest-virginia-remote-work-program-mortgage-assistance-2021-9%5C%22%3Eso%20many%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%207%2C500%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20state%20partnered%20with%20Rocket%20Mortgage%20to%20offer%20the%20applicants%20that%20were%20not%20selected%20for%20the%20program%20%242%2C500%20to%20put%20