0stock%20market%20will%20'zig-zag'%205%25%20higher%20toward%20new%20record%20levels%20in%20December%2C%20Fundstrat%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225383%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tom%20Lee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5faa98cdf7d1cb0019e3abd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222691%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECindy%20Ord%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20stock%20market%20is%20poised%20to%20jump%205%25%20in%20December%20to%20test%20record%20highs%2C%20according%20to%20Fundstrat's%20Tom%20Lee.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20straight%20line%20higher%2C%20and%20the%20upcoming%20jobs%20and%20inflation%20reports%20could%20spark%20a%20temporary%20sell-off.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELee%20said%20investors%20should%20buy%20any%20potential%20dip%20in%20stocks%20as%20the%20second%20half%20of%20December%20should%20be%20filled%20with%20gains.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20market%20is%20poised%20to%20%26quot%3Bzig-zag%26quot%3B%20towards%20record%20highs%20in%20December%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20rising%205%25%20to%204%2C800%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Monday%20note%20from%20Fundstrat's%20Tom%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20gain%20would%20put%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20within%20spitting%20distance%20of%20its%20January%202022%20all-time%20intraday%20high%20of%204%2C818%2C%20and%20just%20above%20its%20record%20closing%20high%20of%204%2C796.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOctober%20personal%20consumption%20expenditures%20price%20data%2C%20set%20to%20be%20released%20on%20Thursday%2C%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bsoft%26quot%3B%20and%20help%20drive%20stocks%20initially%20higher%2C%20according%20to%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20doesn't%20expect%20the%20stock%20market's%20potential%20gains%20over%20the%20next%20month%20to%20happen%20in%20a%20straight%20line%2C%20and%20said%20there%20could%20be%20downside%20volatility%20driven%20by%20upcoming%20jobs%20and%20consumer%20inflation%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20those%20two%20reports%2C%20scheduled%20to%20be%20released%20on%20December%208%20and%20December%2012%2C%20come%20in%20higher%20than%20consensus%20estimates%2C%20they%20would%20likely%20send%20bond%20yields%20up%20and%20stock%20prices%20down%20as%20it%20would%20put%20investors%20on%20edge%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20further%20rate%20hikes%20by%20the%20Federal%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20for%20the%20'zig-zag'%20is%20that%20we%20know%20rates%20markets%20is%20still%20hyperreactive%20to%20the%20opposing%20forces%20of%20'falling%20goods%20and%20housing%20inflation'%20against%20resilient%20labor%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20strong%20jobs%20report%20could%20be%20in%20the%20cards%20because%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20auto%20workers%20were%20rehired%20in%20November%20following%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuaw-strike-contract-raises-pay-details-ford-gm-stellantis-2023-10%5C%22%3Ethe%20end%20of%20strikes%20against%20General%20Motors%2C%20Ford%2C%20and%20Stellantis.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20any%20stock%20market%20declines%20on%20the%20November%20jobs%20and%20inflation%20reports%20will%20likely%20be%20short-lived%20and%20Lee%20recommends%20investors%20buy%20the%20dip.%20That's%20because%20incoming%20data%20continues%20to%20support%20a%20soft-landing%20scenario%20for%20the%20economy%2C%20even%20as%20investors%20continue%20to%20be%20laser-focused%20on%20a%20potential%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20buying%20dips%20if%20the%20markets%20see%20selling%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-friday-record-sales-mobile-phones-2023-11%5C%22%3Esolid%20Black%20Friday%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20positive%20sign%20because%20it%20shows%20continued%20resilience%20in%20the%20consumer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20catalyst%20for%20a%20continued%20move%20higher%20in%20stock%20prices%20next%20month%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20on%20December%2013%2C%20when%20the%20Fed%20holds%20its%20FOMC%20meeting%20and%20press%20conference%2C%20according%20to%20Lee.%20Fed%20Chairman%20Jerome%20Powell%20is%20expected%20to%20leave%20interest%20rates%20unchanged%2C%20and%20Lee%20said%20he%20sees%20room%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bdovish%20shift%26quot%3B%20among%20the%20Fed%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20he%20highlighted%20that%20despite%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20surging%2020%25%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20investors%20have%20pulled%20%24240%20billion%20from%20equity%20mutual%20funds%20and%20ETFs.%20That%20money%20could%20serve%20as%20buying%20power%20for%20investors%20who%20missed%20out%20on%20this%20year's%20rally%20and%20decide%20to%20chase%20equities%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-zig-zag-record-highs-buy-dip-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701098268000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fdb8bb8c910a400192e814f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-zig-zag-record-highs-buy-dip-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20stock%20market%20declines%20on%20the%20November%20jobs%20and%20inflation%20reports%20will%20likely%20be%20short-lived%2C%20and%20Fundstrat%20recommends%20investors%20buy%20the%20dip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-zig-zag-record-highs-buy-dip-2023-11%22%