s%20monitoring%20and%20forecasting%20weather%20events.%20Today%2C%20it%20puts%20a%20lot%20more%20effort%20into%20research%20on%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20big%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20Mandous%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20citing%20the%20WMO's%20numerous%20weather%20stations%2C%20data%20centers%2C%20and%20radar%20networks.%20%26quot%3BThis%20should%20be%20used%20for%20the%20climate.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Mandous'%20goals%20is%20to%20turn%20the%20Early%20Warnings%20for%20All%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20a%20project%20that%20provides%20warning%20systems%20for%20communities%20at%20risk%20of%20extreme%20weather%20events%20%E2%80%94%20into%20reality.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20hoped%20to%20secure%20funding%20at%20the%20upcoming%20COP28%20conference%20to%20%26quot%3Bclose%20the%20gap%20of%20monitoring%26quot%3B%20in%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20missing%20gaps%20in%20the%20countries%2C%20especially%20in%20Africa%20and%20small%20islands%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20initiate%20alarm%20systems%20that%20will%20warn%20those%20countries%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mandous%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%20data-image-ids%3D%5C%22%5B%26quot%3B655a62249c7d23cb3b9d2460%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655a62249c7d23cb3b9d245e%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655a62249c7d23cb3b9d2463%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655a62249c7d23cb3b9d245f%26quot%3B%5D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cpicture%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655a62249c7d23cb3b9d245e%3Fwidth%3D350%26amp%3Bauto%3Dwebp%26amp%3Bquality%3D100%2C100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abdulla%20Al%20Mandous%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fpicture%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAndrew%20Baker%2C%20Professor%2C%20University%20of%20Miami%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2