ied%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fnews-and-stories%2Fstory%2Fwhat-you-need-know-about-cop27-loss-and-damage-fund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELoss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20at%20COP27%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20support%20the%20countries%20that%20are%20harmed%20the%20most%20by%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis%20and%20to%20force%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fenvironment%2F2023%2Fjun%2F15%2Ffossil-fuel-lobbyists-will-have-to-identify-themselves-when-registering-for-cop28%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efossil-fuel%20lobbyists%20to%20identify%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20registering%20for%20COP28.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiddiqa%20currently%20serves%20as%20a%20youth%20climate%20advisor%20to%20the%20UN%20secretary-general.%20She's%20also%20on%20the%20steering%20committee%20of%20the%20Youth%20Climate%20Justice%20Fund%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20youth-led%20regranter%20in%20the%20climate%20space%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20it%20secures%20grants%20to%20issue%20them%20to%20others.%20Looking%20ahead%2C%20she%20wants%20to%20continue%20her%20legislative%20work%20and%20help%20protect%20the%20planet%20for%20future%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20urgency%20of%20the%20situation%20is%20what%20keeps%20Siddiqa%20going.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20more%20to%20lose%2C%20and%20nothing%20more%20left%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%20data-image-ids%3D%5C%22%5B%26quot%3B655abfc722cf74a57399e927%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655abfc722cf74a57399e926%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655abfc722cf74a57399e929%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655abfc722cf74a57399e928%26quot%3B%5D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cpicture%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655abfc722cf74a57399e926%3Fwidth%3D350%26amp%3Baut