r%20GRI%2C%20standards%20in%20Singapore%20in%202008%20and%20it%20remains%20an%20important%20part%20of%20her%20approach.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20measure%2C%20you%20can't%20manage%2C%26quot%3B%20An%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20also%20passionate%20about%20education%20and%20empowerment.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20particularly%20proud%20of%20the%20CDL%20Green%20Gallery%20at%20the%20Singapore%20Botanic%20Gardens%20Heritage%20Museum%2C%20which%20hosts%20exhibitions%20about%20the%20climate%20crisis%20and%20sustainable%20living.%20An%20said%20that%20the%20gallery%20is%20%26quot%3Bnet%20zero%26quot%3B%20and%20runs%20on%20solar%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%20data-image-ids%3D%5C%22%5B%26quot%3B655ad1ad4ca513d8242c02d3%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655ad1ad22cf74a57399ec62%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655ad1ad22cf74a57399ec63%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655ad1ad4ca513d8242c02d4%26quot%3B%5D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cpicture%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655ad1ad22cf74a57399ec62%3Fwidth%3D350%26amp%3Bauto%3Dwebp%26amp%3Bquality%3D100%2C100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Esther%20An%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fpicture%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELisa%20P.%20Jackson%2C%20Vice%20president%2C%20Environment%2C%20Policy%20and%20Social%20Initiatives%2C%20Apple%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224668%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Lisa%20P.%20Jackson%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20a%20long%20maroon%20dress%20in%20front%20of%20a%20green%20landscape.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6552595058cf5fbccb959613%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EApple%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20P.%20Jackson%20has%20always%20been%20driven%20by%20her%20desire%20to%20protect%20people%20and%20the%20planet.%20%26quot%3BDevastating%20storms%20like%20Katrina%20that%20destroyed%20the%20home%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20have%20shown%20us%20the%20consequences%20of%20inaction%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackson%2C%20who%20has%20a%20background%20in%20chemical%20engineering%2C%20had%20a%20two-decade%20career%20in%20public%20service%20before%20joining%20the%20corporate%20world.%20She%20served%20under%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20as%20the%20administrator%20of%20the%20Environment%20Protection%20Agency%2C%20where%20she%20led%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2010%2F05%2F25%2F127105123%2Fepa-pressures-bp-to-reduce-toxic-dispersant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20EPA's%20response%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Deepwater%20Horizon%20oil%20spill%2C%20took%20action%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fobamawhitehouse.archives.gov%2Fblog%2Fauthor%2Fadministrator-lisa-p-jackson%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20and%20water%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20made%20environmental%20justice%20a%20key%20priority.%20She%20joined%20Apple%20in%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20entire%20career%20has%20been%20motivated%20by%20the%20mission%20to%20protect%20people's%20health%20and%20the%20environment%20was%20a%20great%20motivator%20for%20me.%20Joining%20Apple%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20continue%20my%20life's%20work%20to%20drive%20climate%20progress%20forward%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20helped%20suppliers%20improve%20sustainability%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20its%20facilities%20have%20run%20on%20100%25%20renewable%20energy%20since%202018%2C%20Jackson%20said.%20While%20Apple%20has%20faced%20criticism%20for%20its%20frequent%20product%20launches%2C%20which%20encourage%20consumers%20to%20upgrade%20their%20devices%20regularly%2C%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20make%20every%20product%20carbon%20neutral%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%20and%20eliminate%20plastic%20packaging%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackson%20also%20leads%20Apple's%20more%20than%20%24200%20million%20global%20Racial%20Equity%20and%20Justice%20Initiative%20to%20expand%20opportunities%20for%20Black%2C%20Hispanic%2C%20Latinx%2C%20and%20Indigenous%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%20data-image-ids%3D%5C%22%5B%26quot%3B655adc719c7d23cb3b9d2e57%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655adc7122cf74a57399ed3a%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655adc7122cf74a57399ed3b%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655adc719c7d23cb3b9d2e58%26quot%3B%5D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cpicture%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655adc7122cf74a57399ed3a%3Fwidth%3D350%26amp%3Bauto%3Dwebp%26amp%3Bquality%3D100%2C100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lisa%20Jackson%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fpicture%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENicole%20Systrom%2C%20Chief%20impact%20officer%2C%20Galvanize%20Climate%20Solutions%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Nicole%20Systrom%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20a%20gray%20plaid%20blazer%20and%20brown%20shirt%20in%20front%20of%20greenery.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e6a6b3cc84b4dfa0036b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222341%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELuci%20Valentine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20role%20as%20chief%20impact%20officer%20at%20Galvanize%20Climate%20Solutions%2C%20a%20climate-focused%20global%20investment%20firm%2C%20Nicole%20Systrom%20leads%20a%20team%20of%20experts%20across%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESystrom%20supports%20investors%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bas%20much%20climate%20impact%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Galvanize%20has%20three%20strategies%20%E2%80%94%20a%20venture%20strategy%2C%20a%20public-equity%20strategy%2C%20and%20a%20real-estate%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20all%20focused%20on%20decarbonization%20in%20different%20ways%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20they'll%20become%20a%20model%20for%20other%20investors%20to%20follow%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Systrom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESystrom%20said%20that%20climate%20technology%20needed%20capital%20to%20close%20the%20%26quot%3Bfinancing%20gap.%26quot%3B%20In%20September%2C%20Galvanize%20announced%20the%20final%20close%20of%20its%20Innovation%20%2B%20Expansion%20Fund%20at%20over%20%241%20billion%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20climate%20venture%20funds%20raised%20to%20date.%20Systrom%20described%20the%20fund%20as%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20remarkable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20all%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20investment%20ecosystem%2C%20all%20different%20asset%20classes%2C%20all%20types%20of%20investors%2C%20really%20activated%20towards%20climate%20transition.%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20role%20for%20every%20type%20of%20investor%20to%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20Systrom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESystrom%20also%20serves%20on%20the%20steering%20committee%20of%20a%20group%20called%20the%20Venture%20Climate%20Alliance%2C%20which%20formed%20in%20April.%20It's%20seeking%20to%20shape%20a%20net-zero%20standard%20for%20the%20venture%20industry%20and%20%26quot%3Btry%20to%20drive%20consensus%20around%20the%20role%20venture%20capitalists%20should%20be%20playing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%20data-image-ids%3D%5C%22%5B%26quot%3B655acd669c7d23cb3b9d2cef%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655acd669c7d23cb3b9d2cf0%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655acd6622cf74a57399eb83%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655acd6622cf74a57399eb82%26quot%3B%5D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cpicture%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655acd669c7d23cb3b9d2cf0%3Fwidt