-extraction%20methods%20require%20vast%20amounts%20of%20land%20and%20water.%20Hall%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20more%20sustainable%20way%20to%20meet%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20the%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESummit%20Nanotech%20employs%20a%20method%20called%20direct%20lithium%20extraction%2C%20which%20uses%20less%20land%20and%20produces%20less%20waste%20than%20traditional%20extraction%20methods%2C%20Hall%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%20there's%20a%20common%20misconception%20that%20cleantech%20is%20costly.%20In%20reality%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20reductions%20in%20energy%20use%2C%20water%20use%2C%20and%20waste%20management%20result%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20cheaper%20process%20that's%20also%20cleaner%20and%20more%20efficient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20opened%20a%20facility%20in%20Chile%20to%20scale%20up%20its%20direct-lithium-extraction%20technology%20following%20a%20pilot%20program%20in%202022.%20For%20Hall%2C%20it%20was%20important%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Bboots%20on%20the%20ground%26quot%3B%20and%20establish%20good%20relationships%20with%20Indigenous%20communities%20in%20Chile%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20also%20worked%20with%20the%20Chilean%20government%20to%20introduce%20new%20standards%20for%20lithium%20extraction%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20legislation%2C%20announced%20in%20April%2C%20implements%20higher%20standards%20for%20things%20such%20as%20water%20and%20energy%20preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%20data-image-ids%3D%5C%22%5B%26quot%3B655cabe622cf74a5739a9f11%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655cabe622cf74a5739a9f12%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655cabe64ca513d8242cb548%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655cabe64ca513d8242cb549%26quot%3B%5D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cpicture%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655cabe622cf74a5739a9f12%3Fwidth%3D350%26amp%3Bauto%3Dwebp%26amp%3Bquality%3D100%2C100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20Hall%5