0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20has%20always%20had%20the%20%26quot%3Bentrepreneurial%20bug%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20but%20he%20was%20inspired%20to%20focus%20on%20solutions%20to%20the%20climate%20crisis%20after%20a%20conversation%20with%20his%20children%20where%20he%20promised%20them%20he%20would%20try%20to%20make%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%20data-image-ids%3D%5C%22%5B%26quot%3B655d383a9c7d23cb3b9e86db%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655d383a22cf74a5739b469d%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655d383a22cf74a5739b469c%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655d383a9c7d23cb3b9e86dc%26quot%3B%5D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cpicture%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d383a22cf74a5739b469d%3Fwidth%3D350%26amp%3Bauto%3Dwebp%26amp%3Bquality%3D100%2C100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rep.%20Sandeep%20Nijhawan%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fpicture%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKimiko%20Hirata%2C%20Executive%20director%2C%20Climate%20Integrate%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Kimiko%20Hirata%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20a%20dark%20cardigan%20in%20front%20of%20greenery.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e5ad53cc84b4dfa001e3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETakao%20Ochi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKimiko%20Hirata's%20work%20as%20an%20activist%20has%20led%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%2017%20planned%20coal%20power%20plants%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Fukushima%20nuclear%20accident%20in%202011%2C%20the%20Japanese%20government%20shut%20down%20many%20of%20its%20nuclear-power%20facilities%20and%20turned%20to%20coal%20power%20to%20provide%20the%20country's%20energy%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Hirata%2C%20who%20holds%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20social%20sciences%20from%20Waseda%20University%2C%20worked%20on%20environmental%20policy%20at%20the%20Japanese%20nonprofit%20Kiko%20Network.%20She%20knew%20that%20the%20expansion%20of%20coal%20power%20would%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20greenhouse-gas%20emissions%20and%20said%20she%20was%20wary%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bno%20voices%20on%20the%20ground%26quot%3B%20to%20fight%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHirata%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20felt%20nongovernmental%20organizations%20and%20civil%20society%20in%20Japan%20were%20too%20small%20to%20stop%20the%20government%20and%20big%20industry%20and%20that%20public%20awareness%20of%20the%20climate%20impact%20of%20coal%20power%20was%20low.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20advertised%20that%20the%20latest%20coal%20power%20is%20clean%2C%20so%20people%20believed%20that%20this%20is%20clean%20and%20there's%20no%20harm%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Japanese%20government%20has%20promoted%20ammonia%20cofiring%2C%20where%20ammonia%20is%20blended%20with%20coal%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bclean%26quot%3B%20despite%20warnings%20that%20the%20method%20does%20little%20to%20affect%20overall%20greenhouse-gas%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHirata%20wanted%20to%20change%20that%2C%20so%20she%20started%20to%20make%20connections%20at%20the%20community%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tried%20several%20different%20approaches%20to%20get%20the%20support%2C%20talking%20about%20air%20pollution%2C%20or%20economic%20impacts%2C%20or%20climate%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Hirata%20said.%20She%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btrial%20and%20error%26quot%3B%20at%20first.%20Gradually%2C%20the%20campaign%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20local%20people%2C%20and%20the%20media%20started%20to%20cover%20the%20story%2C%20which%20Hirata%20said%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bgame%20changer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHirata%20said%20that%20while%20she%20%26quot%3Bplanted%20the%20seeds%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20campaign%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20success%20was%20made%20by%20local%20people's%20voice%20and%20power.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Hirata%20runs%20Climate%20Integrate%2C%20a%20think%20tank%2C%20because%20she%20wants%20to%20increase%20climate%20expertise%20in%20Japan.%20She's%20also%20running%20a%20new%20campaign%20based%20around%20shareholder%20activism%2C%20a%20type%20of%20activism%20that%20targets%20fossil-fuel%20financers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%20data-image-ids%3D%5C%22%5B%26quot%3B655d2bfc4ca513d8242d5829%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655d2bfc4ca513d8242d582a%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655d2bfc22cf74a5739b4074%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B655d2bfc22cf74a5739b4075%26quot%3B%5D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cpicture%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d2bfc4ca513d8242d582a%3Fwidth%3D350%26amp%3Bauto%3Dwebp%26amp%3Bquality%3D100%2C100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kimiko%20Hirata%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fpicture%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMia%20Mottley%2C%20Prime%20minister%2C%20Barbados%20Caribbean%20Government%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222806%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Mia%20Mottley%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20silver%20earrings%20and%20a%20white%20blouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e623bb788914e55540843%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224209%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJOEL%20SAGET%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMia%20Mottley%20became%20Barbados'%20first%20woman%20prime%20minister%20in%202018.%20The%20politician%20and%20lawyer%20broke%20political%20glass%20ceilings%20earlier%20in%20her%20career%2C%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Barbados%20Labour%20Party%20and%20as%20attorney%20general.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMottley%20has%20made%20a%20name%20for%20herself%20by%20calling%20out%20wealthy%20n