0money%20to%20make%20money%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20%3Cem%3Eyour%20%3C%2Fem%3Emoney%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real-estate%20investors%20and%20entrepreneurs%20I'm%20talking%20to%20who%20are%20building%20long-term%20wealth%20are%20doing%20so%20by%20putting%20money%20to%20work%20%E2%80%94%20by%20investing%20in%20properties%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20the%20stock%20market.%20As%20the%20adage%20goes%2C%20you%20need%20money%20to%20make%20money.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20necessarily%20have%20to%20be%20%3Cem%3Eyour%20%3C%2Fem%3Emoney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReal-estate%20investors%20Natia%20and%20Jervais%20Seegars%20explained%20to%20me%20the%20concept%20of%20using%20%26quot%3Bother%20people's%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20OPM%2C%20to%20build%20wealth.%20By%20raising%20money%20from%20investors%20to%20buy%20properties%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20were%20able%20to%20continue%20to%20save%20our%20money%20while%20using%20other%20people's%20money%20to%20make%20us%20more%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20how%20the%20college%20dropouts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvest-in-real-estate-with-zero-money-upfront-seller-financing-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECaleb%20Hommel%20and%20Chuck%20Sotelo%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20funded%20their%20first%20deal%20as%20teenagers%20without%20savings%20or%20a%20credit%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsking%20for%20money%20requires%20putting%20yourself%20out%20there%2C%20a%20thick%20skin%2C%20and%20being%20okay%20with%20hearing%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20say%20%26quot%3Bno.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20requires%20a%20plan.%20The%20strategy%20the%20young%20business%20partners%20live%20by%20is%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20deal%20always%20comes%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hommel.%20If%20you%20find%20a%20good%20enough%20deal%20and%20present%20it%20accurately%20and%20professionally%20to%20investors%2C%20the%20money%20will%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20real-estate%20investor