0professors%20at%20the%20Arab%20American%20University%20of%20Palestine%20in%20Ramallah%2C%20Dalal%20Iriqat.%20The%20plan%20is%20to%20push%20up%20to%202%20million%20Palestinians%2C%20sheltering%20in%20south%20Gaza%2C%20into%20a%20small%20portion%20called%20al-Mawasi%2C%20which%20is%20just%202.5%20kilometres%20wide%20and%204%20kilometres%20long.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Director%20of%20Communications%20of%20UNRWA%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20agency%20responsible%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20Juliette%20Touma%2C%20says%20of%20al-Mawasi%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20there.%20It%20is%20just%20sand%20dunes%20and%20palm%20trees.%E2%80%9D%20Even%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20spokesperson%2C%20Lt.%20Col.%20Richard%20Hecht%2C%20has%20admitted%20al-Mawasi%20is%20%E2%80%9Cgoing%20to%20be%20dire%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FuBmC7JqEorU%3Fsi%3DDrTun4mUkY8KQyGx%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Mawasi%20lacks%20essential%20infrastructure.%20There%20are%20no%20hospitals%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20people%2C%20if%20pushed%20there%2C%20will%20have%20to%20live%20in%20tents.%20This%20will%20be%20at%20a%20time%20when%20winter%20has%20set%20in%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20cold%20and%20it%20rains%20frequently.%20Yet%2C%20Avichay%20Adraee%2C%20an%20Israeli%20defence%20forces%20spokesman%20has%20told%20the%20Arabic%20media%20(as%20reported%20by%20Paul%20Adams%20in%20his%20BBC%20story)%20al-Mawasi%20will%20provide%20%E2%80%9Cappropriate%20conditions%20for%20your%20loved%20ones%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdam%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CIsraeli%20officials%20say%20it%20will%20be%20up%20to%20aid%20agencies%20to%20make%20sure%20hel