ols-dont-die%2Farticleshow%2F105538027.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seven%20Kashmiri%20Students%20Arrested%20Over%20'Pro-Pakistan'%20Slogans%20After%20India's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20Loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20124329%2FF_TytKoWgAALbGm.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20have%20arrested%20seven%20Kashmiri%20students%20under%20an%20anti-terror%20law%20for%20allegedly%20shouting%20pro-Pakistan%20slogans%20after%20India%E2%80%99s%20loss%20to%20Australia%20during%20the%20finals%20of%20the%20recently%20concluded%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20Ganderbal%20police%20station%20under%20Section%2013%20(advocating%2C%20abetting%20or%20inciting%20any%20unlawful%20activity)%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA)%20and%20Sections%20505%20(inciting%20communal%20violence)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20November%2019%20at%20one%20of%20the%20two%20undergraduate%20hostels%20of%20the%20Sher-e-Kashmir%20University%20of%20Agriculture%20Science%20and%20Technology%20in%20the%20Ganderbal%20district%2C%20after%20India%20lost%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20finals.%20They%20said%20that%20there%20was%20sloganeering%20allegedly%20inside%20the%20hostel%2C%20where%20some%20local%20students%20stay.%20The%20alleged%20slogan-shouting%20was%20filmed%20by%20non-local%20students%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20complaint%20by%20Sachin%20Bains%2C%20a%20student%20of%20the%20Faculty%20of%20Veterinary%20Science%20and%20Animal%20Husbandry%20at%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspects%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Umer%2C%20Asif%2C%20Mohsin%2C%20Tauqeer%2C%20Khali%2C%20Sameer%2C%20and%20Ubaid%20Gulzar%20who%20are%20enrolled%20in%20different%20courses%20at%20the%20university.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20completing%20their%20degrees%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20complainant%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20was%20allegedly%20abused%20and%20threatened%20by%20the%20students%20purportedly%20over%20rooting%20for%20India%20during%20the%20final%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20was%20clinched%20by%20Australia%20by%20six%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Punjab%2C%20also%20alleged%20to%20the%20police%20that%20the%20students%20shouted%20pro-Pakistan%20slogans%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Jeeve%20Jeeve%20Pakistan%E2%80%99%20which%20created%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20among%20the%20non-local%20students%20at%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperintendent%20of%20Police%20Nikhil%20Borkar%20Ganderbal%20told%20%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Csome%20sections%20are%20added%20or%20deleted%20depending%20upon%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20investigation%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20investigation%20is%20on%20and%20whatever%20will%20be%20there%2C%20we%20will%20let%20you%20know%20at%20that%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Borkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701091558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20124329%2FF_TytKoWgAALbGm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fseven-kashmiri-students-arrested-over-pro-pakistan-slogans-after-indias-cricket-world-cup-loss%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20incident%20allegedly%20took%20place%20at%20an%20undergraduate%20hostel%20of%20the%20Sher-e-Kashmir%20University%20in%20Ganderbal%20district%20after%20India%20lost%20World%20Cup%20final%20to%20Australia%20on%20November%2019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fseven-kashmiri-students-arrested-over-pro-pakistan-slogans-after-indias-cricket-world-cup-loss%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Money%20For%20Ads%2C%20Not%20For%20Infrastructure%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%20rapped%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20Delhi%20for%20not%20releasing%20funds%20for%20the%20Regional%20Rapid%20Transit%20System%20(RRTS)%20project.%20While%20directing%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20immediately%20transfer%20the%20money%20to%20National%20Capital%20Region%20Transport%20Corporation%20(NCRTC)%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20remarked%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20such%20national%20projects%20are%20affected%2C%20and%20if%20the%20money%20is%20being%20spent%20on%20advertisement%2C%20we%20would%20be%20inclined%20to%20ask%20the%20money%20to%20be%20directed%20to%20infrastructure.%26quot%3B%20The%20apex%20court%20said%20if%20the%20Delhi%20government%20didn't%20comply%20with%20the%20direction%20within%20a%20week%2C%20the%20order%20would%20come%20into%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20was%20hearing%20petitions%20filed%20after%20the%20spike%20in%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20capital.%20The%20RRTS%20project%20is%20meant%20to%20reduce%20vehicular%20pollution%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region.%20In%20a%20recent%20collaboration%20between%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20IIT-Kanpur%2C%20findings%20revealed%20that%20vehicular%20emissions%20contributed%20to%20approximately%2038%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20capital's%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20RRTS%20Project%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20augment%20connectivity%20within%20Delhi-NCR%20and%20reduce%20the%20commuters'%20dependency%20on%20road%20transport%2C%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20Planning%20Board%20(NCRPB)%20had%20proposed%20to%20connect%20urban%2C%20industrial%20(SEZs%2Findustrial%20parks)%2C%20regional%20and%20sub-regional%20centres%20through%20a%20fast%20rail-based%20system.%20The%20RRTS%20will%20lessen%20travel%20time%2C%20pollution%20and%20congestion%20created%20by%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20vehicles.%20The%20NCRPB%20conducted%20a%20study%20on%20an%20Integrated%20Transportation%20Plan%20for%20NCR%20projecting%20figures%20for%202032%2C%20and%20identified%20eight%20rail-based%20rapid%20transit%20corridors%20to%20enhance%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20transport%20system%20in%20the%20NCR.%20Three%20corridors%2C%20Delhi-Meerut%2C%20Delhi-Panipat%20and%20Delhi-%20Alwar%2C%20are%20being%20built%20in%20Phase%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rail%20corridor%20called%20RAPIDX%20will%20connect%20Delhi%2C%20Ghaziabad%20and%20Meerut.%20The%20Delhi-Meerut%20corridor%20is%20nearly%2082%20km%20in%20length.%20The%20estimated%20cost%20of%20the%20project%2C%20per%20a%202019%20court%20document%2C%20was%20Rs%2031%2C%20632%20crores%20with%2060%3A40%20debt%20equity%20ratio.%20The%20central%20government%20and%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Government%20have%20given%20their%20share%20and%20the%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%20has%20decided%20to%20furnish%20the%20debt%20part.%20The%20contribution%20of%20the%20Central%20government%20to%20the%20project%20is%20Rs%205%2C687%20crore%2C%20that%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20Rs%205%2C828%20crore%20and%20Delhi's%20is%20Rs%201%2C138%20crore.%20Once%20operational%2C%20the%20first%20RRTS%20corridor%20is%20estimated%20to%20reduce%202%2C50%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20in%20vehicular%20emissions%20per%20year.%20An%20estimated%20daily%20ridership%20on%20the%2082-km%20Delhi-Ghaziabad-Meerut%20corridor%20is%208%20lakhs.%20Once%20the%20RAPIDX%20becomes%20functional%2C%20it%20will%20take%20more%20than%20one%20lakh%20vehicles%20off%20the%20road.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%2017-km%20priority%20section%20of%20the%20Delhi-Ghaziabad-Meerut%20RRTS%20Corridor%20on%20October%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ongoing%20controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20agreed%20to%20make%20budgetary%20provisions%20to%20hand%20over%20its%20share%20of%20funds%20for%20the%20RRTS%20project.%20The%20AAP%20government%2C%20however%2C%20reneged%20on%20its%20promise%20and%20expressed%20its%20helplessness%20in%20the%20court.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20said%20it%20had%20no%20funds%20to%20contribute%20its%20share%20of%20Rs%203%2C261%20crore%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Delhi-Gurugram-Rewari-Alwar%20corridor%20and%20Rs%202%2C443%20crore%20for%20the%20Delhi-Sonipat-Panipat%20corridor.%20The%20NCRTC%20then%20filed%20an%20application%20alleging%20breach%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20undertaking%20to%20the%20court%20on%20July%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtmaram%20NS%20Nadkarni%2C%20the%20senior%20Supreme%20Court%20advocate%20who%20represented%20the%20NCRTC%2C%20said%20Article%2021%20was%20interpreted%20to%20mean%20an%20injunction%20against%20the%20state%20assuring%20citizens%20the%20right%20to%20breathe%20clean%20air%20free%20of%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20most%20unfortunate%20that%20any%20state%20or%20government%20can%20afford%20to%20have%20such%20a%20casual%20lackadaisical%20approach%20in%20such%20important%20matters.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20done%20a%20great%20job%20in%20securing%20the%20forest%20cover%20of%20our%20country.%20This%20order%20will%20be%20an%20eye%20opener%20for%20all%20states%20and%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadkarni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20treated%20the%20right%20to%20live%20in%20a%20pollution-free%20environment%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20fundamental%20Right%20to%20Life%20under%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20upset%20at%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Government%20argued%20shortage%20of%20funds%20even%20though%20it%20had%20some%20Rs%201%2C100%20crore%20to%20spend%20on%20its%20advertisements.%20In%20the%20ongoing%20financial%20year%20too%2C%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal-led%20government%20in%20Delhi%20assigned%20Rs%20550%20crore%20in%20the%20budget%20for%20advertisements.%20This%20was%20much%20more%20than%20the%20amount%20the%20Delhi%20government%20had%20to%20pay%20to%20cover%20its%20share%20of%20expenditure%20on%20the%20RRTS%20project.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20was%20to%20pay%20Rs%20415%20crore%20for%20the%20crucial%20infrastructure%20project.%20It%20agreed%20to%20pay%20its%20portion%20for%20the%20Delhi-Meerut%20stretch%2C%20but%20declined%20to%20shoulder%20the%20financial%20burden%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20stretches%20citing%20lack%20of%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajeshwar%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20a%20journalist%2C%20lives%20in%20Noida%20but%20travels%20to%20Delhi%20for%20work.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20citizen%20of%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20I%20find%20it%20frustrating%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20doesn't%20have%20funds%20to%20spend%20on%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20the%20railroad%2C%20which%20will%20benefit%20people%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20Not%20only%20will%20commuting%20become%20easy%20but%20also%20less%20vehicles%20will%20ply%20on%20roads%2C%20which%20means%20less%20pollution.%20Pollution%20is%20choking%20and%20shortening%20lives%20and%20the%20Delhi%20government%20is%20delaying%20the%20project%20while%20splashing%20money%20on%20advertisements%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi-NCR%20region%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20most%20polluted%20in%20the%20world%20and%20vehicular%20pollution%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20main%20contributing%20factors.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20has%20been%20collecting%20a%20cess%20-%20ECC%20(environment%20compensation%20charge)%20-%20imposed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20diesel%20cars%20above%202000%20cc%20in%20order%20to%20check%20pollution.%20Earlier%2C%20from%20the%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20collected%20in%20this%20cess%20fund%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20allowed%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20use%20Rs%20500%20crore%20to%20fund%20the%20Delhi-Meerut%20corridor%20as%20the%20project%20was%20being%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20worrying%20and%20shocking%20is%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20effort%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20AAP-led%20government%20to%20make%20budgetary%20allocations%20for%20the%20project.%20AAP%20leaders%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%20don't%20shy%20away%20from%20making%20tall%20claims%20about%20being%20different%20and%20bringing%20change%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20common%20man.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20has%20exposed%20the%20reality%20and%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20lack%20of%20intention%20or%20inclination%20to%20contribute%20its%20share%20in%20an%20infrastructure%20project%20like%20the%20RRTS%20project%2C%20which%20will%20help%20eliminate%20one%20of%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20the%20perpetual%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701091380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F84kga5j8_delhi-rrts-ani_625x300_27_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmoney-for-ads-not-for-infrastructure-4610580%22%2C%2