s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fananya-panday-reacts-to-paparazzi-calling-her-anna-watch%2Farticleshow%2F105537834.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GT%20Break%20Silence%20On%20Hardik's%20Move%20To%20MI%2C%20Explain%20Reason%20Behind%20Trade%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Titans%20on%20Monday%20appointed%20Shubman%20Gill%20as%20their%20captain%20for%20the%202024%20season%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20following%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20decision%20to%20move%20back%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20The%20Gujarat%20Titans%20will%20receive%20Rs%2015%20crore%20from%20MI%20for%20the%20all-cash%20trade%20deal%20apart%20from%20a%20hefty%20undisclosed%20transfer%20fee%2C%20a%20part%20of%20which%20will%20also%20go%20to%20the%20cricketer.%20Once%20Pandya's%20exit%20was%20sure%2C%2024-year-old%20opener%20Gill%20was%20an%20obvious%20captaincy%20choice%2C%20having%20got%20the%20coveted%20'orange%20cap'%20in%20the%20last%20season%20with%20890%20runs%2C%20second%20to%20only%20Virat%20Kohli's%20all-time%20record%20of%20973.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20delighted%20and%20proud%20to%20assume%20the%20captaincy%20of%20Gujarat%20Titans%20and%20thank%20the%20franchise%20for%20their%20trust%20in%20me%20to%20lead%20such%20a%20fine%20team.%20We%20have%20had%20two%20exceptional%20seasons%20and%20I%20keenly%20look%20forward%20to%20leading%20the%20team%20with%20our%20exciting%20brand%20of%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Gill%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%2C%20on%20his%20part%2C%20took%20to%20'X'%2C%20formerly%20twitter%20to%20express%20his%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20brings%20back%20so%20many%20wonderful%20memories.%20Mumbai.%20Wankhede.%20Paltan.%20Feels%20good%20to%20be%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20commented%20on%20'X'%20on%20a%20video%20depicting%20his%20entire%20journey%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGT%20Team%20Director%20Vikram%20Solanki%20acknowledged%20Pandya's%20contribution%20to%20the%20team's%20success%20in%20then%20last%20two%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20first%20captain%20of%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20has%20helped%20the%20franchise%20deliver%20two%20fantastic%20seasons%20that%20resulted%20in%20winning%20one%20IPL%20championship%20and%20one%20appearance%20in%20the%20final%2C%26quot%3B%20Solanki%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20now%20expressed%20a%20desire%20to%20return%20to%20his%20original%20team%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20We%20respect%20his%20decision%20and%20wish%20him%20all%20the%20very%20best%20in%20his%20future%20endeavours%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20England%20batter%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolanki%2C%20who%20has%20closely%20worked%20with%20Gill%2C%20vouched%20for%20his%20maturity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShubman%20Gill%20has%20shown%20growth%20in%20stature%20and%20standing%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20the%20game.%20We've%20seen%20him%20mature%20not%20only%20as%20a%20batter%20but%20also%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Solanki%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20maturity%20and%20skill%20is%20evident%20in%20his%20on-field%20performance%20and%20we%20are%20extremely%20excited%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20new%20journey%20with%20a%20young%20leader%20like%20Shubman%20at%20the%20helm%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20head%20of%20GT%20think-tank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThrilled%20to%20welcome%20back%20Hardik%2C%20says%20MI%20owners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20owners%20Nita%20Ambani%20and%20Akash%20Ambani%20both%20termed%20Pandya's%20return%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20homecoming%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20welcome%20Hardik%20back%20home!%20It's%20a%20heartwarming%20reunion%20with%20our%20Mumbai%20Indians%20family!%20From%20being%20a%20young%20scouted%20talent%20of%20Mumbai%20Indians%20to%20now%20being%20a%20team%20India%20star%2C%20Hardik%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20and%20we're%20excited%20for%20what%20the%20future%20holds%20for%20him%20and%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Ambani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20son%20Akash%20spoke%20about%20the%20balance%20that%20the%20all-rounder%20lends%20to%20any%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20happy%20homecoming.%20He%20provides%20great%20balance%20to%20any%20team%20he%20plays.%20Hardik's%20first%20stint%20with%20the%20MI%20family%20was%20hugely%20successful%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20he%20achieves%20even%20more%20success%20in%20his%20second%20stint%2C%26quot%3B%20Ambani%20junior%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701090840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fv9444sl_hardik-pandya-_625x300_14_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgujarat-titans-break-silence-on-hardik-pandyas-move-to-mumbai-indians-explains-reason-behind-ipl-trade-deal-4610126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Titans%20appointed%20Shubman%20Gill%20following%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20decision%20to%20move%20back%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgujarat-titans-break-silence-on-hardik-pandyas-move-to-mumbai-indians-explains-reason-behind-ipl-trade-deal-4610126%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgujarat-titans-break-silence-on-hardik-pandyas-move-to-mumbai-indians-explains-reason-behind-ipl-trade-deal-4610126%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgujarat-titans-break-silence-on-hardik-pandyas-move-to-mumbai-indians-explains-reason-behind-ipl-trade-deal-4610126%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Know%20all%20about%20Welcome%20to%20Samdalri%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22p