ear-ago%26userId%3D7302199%26signature%3D42375cb9c0250b3e%5C%22%3Egave%20a%20fresh%20investment%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20project%20at%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20business%20event%2C%20Bengal%20Global%20Business%20Summit%20(BGBS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20first%20deep%20sea%20port%20at%20Tajpur%20is%20ready.%20You%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20tender.%20It%20will%20attract%20an%20investment%20of%20about%20%243%20billion%2C%20meaning%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20Banerjee%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20journalists%20asked%20Panja%20if%20her%20statement%20contradicted%20that%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20honourable%20chief%20minister.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Port%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20(APSEZ)%20head%20Karan%20Adani%20received%20a%20Letter%20of%20Intent%20from%20the%20state%20government%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lack%20of%20consistency%20between%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group%20regarding%20the%20status%20of%20the%20projects%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20state%20government%20had%20on%20several%20occasions%20said%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%20to%20do%20their%20part%20regarding%20necessary%20permissions%20from%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20had%20said%20at%20least%20three%20times%20that%20they%20were%20awaiting%20the%20Letter%20of%20Award%20(LoA)%20from%20the%20government%20to%20start%20with%20the%20other%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20surprise%20announcement%20on%20November%2021%20prompted%20many%20to%20speculate%20if%20this%20was%20the%20fallout%20of%20a%20political%20tussle%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20involving%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20allegedly%20anti-Adani%E2%80%99s%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20public%20backing%20of%20Moitra%20the%20very%20next%20day%20strengthened%20the%20speculations.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20she%20(Moitra)%20used%20to%20say%20inside%2C%20she%20will%20not%20be%20saying%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Banerjee%20had%20said%20at%20a%20party%20event.%20Moitra%20is%20known%20for%20regularly%20accusing%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20giving%20undue%20favours%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20as%20part%20of%20a%20nexus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20participation%20in%20the%20tender%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Dilip%20Ghosh%2C%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Adani%20Group%20that%20backed%20out%20of%20the%20project%20because%20of%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Panja%20said%2C%20reading%20out%20from%20a%20written%20statement%2C%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20was%20%E2%80%9Cgiven%20a%20provisional%20LoI%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20work%20for%20getting%20permissions%20required%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20ministries%20like%20shipping%2C%20home%2C%20defence%20and%20external%20affairs%20%E2%80%9Care%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20has%20given%20a%20conditional%20security%20clearance%20and%20has%20made%20some%20observations.%20We%20are%20working%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group%20regarding%20those%20observations%20and%20have%20asked%20for%20some%20clarifications.%20These%20communications%20are%20going%20on%20currently%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbengali.abplive.com%2Fvideos%2Fdistrict%2Ftmc-leader-sashi-panja-said-talks-are-going-on-with-adani-about-building-a-port-at-tajpur-1027030%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20at%20the%20BGBS%20triggered%20speculations%20over%20whether%20the%20group%20had%20%E2%80%9Csnubbed%E2%80%9D%20the%20government%20because%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20political%20attacks%20alleging%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnexus%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20business%20group%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Panja%20asserted%20that%20the%20government%20had%20sent%20invites%20to%20the%20group%20for%20the%20business%20summit%2C%20a%20senior%20government%20official%2C%20who%20was%20unwilling%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CInvite%20was%20sent%20as%20part%20of%20formality.%20The%20extra%20efforts%20that%20we%20usually%20make%20to%20ensure%20top%20industrialists%E2%80%99%20presence%20were%20not%20made%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%20this%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Panja%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20CPI(M)%20central%20committee%20member%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%20took%20potshots%20at%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20statements%20of%20Panja%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20are%20contradictory.%20They%20(the%20TMC)%20are%20sometimes%20speaking%20up%20against%20Adani%20to%20hide%20their%20own%20nexus.%20But%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20she%20(Banerjee)%20cannot%20go%20beyond%20what%20Delhi%20(BJP)%20tells%20her%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664107%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20Adani%20building%20in%20Australia.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FRegionalQueenslander%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Important%20for%20both%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kolkata-based%20business%20and%20political%20observers%2C%20the%20Tajpur%20port%20project%20is%20important%20to%20both%20the%20state%20government%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20biggest%20industrial%20project%20the%20state%20government%20has%20taken%20up%20during%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%2012-year%20rule%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20the%20proposed%20coal%20mine%20at%20Deucha-Pachami%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20work%20related%20to%20Tajpur%20port%20has%20progressed%20more%20than%20the%20coal%20mine%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20to%20smoothen%20the%20process%20of%20the%20port%20development%2C%20had%20also%20scrapped%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20only%20proposed%20solar%20project%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Rs%20750%20crore%20project%20to%20develop%20a%20125-megawatt%20(MW)%20capacity%20solar%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20had%20received%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20preparing%20a%20detailed%20project%20report%20for%20the%20solar%20park.%20The%20report%20was%20complete%20and%20the%20process%20of%20securing%20an%20international%20loan%20had%20progressed.%20However%2C%20in%202021%2C%20the%20state%20government%20decided%20to%20prioritise%20the%20Tajpur%20project%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20532-acre%20plot%20at%20Dadanpatrabar%20earmarked%20for%20the%20solar%20park%20to%20the%20Tajpur%20port%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20expedited%20the%20development%20of%20industrial%20corridors%2C%20including%20one%20from%20Tajpur%20to%20Dankuni%20near%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20concession%20agreements%20being%20signed%20between%20governments%20and%20private%20industries%20for%20the%20development%2C%20operation%20and%20maintenance%20of%20different%20new%20ports%20and%20terminals%20in%20the%20country%20are%20usually%20for%20a%20period%20of%2030%20years%2C%20whereas%20in%20some%20cases%20a%20period%20of%20up%20to%2050%20years%20is%20being%20considered.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20had%20in%20August%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-ports-for-minimum-50yrs-of-concession-period-in-ppp-projects-11186601.html%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20favour%20of%2050-year%20concession%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20the%2099-year%20concession%20period%20offered%20by%20the%20state%20government%20%E2%80%9Cis%20lucrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20a%20senior%20business%20journalist%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Port%E2%80%99s%20brochure%20published%20in%20August%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FAdani%2Fdownloads%2FAdani-Ports-Brochure-August-2023.pdf%3Fla%3Den%26hash%3DA13AB50213B3EEBA948CF1FFA6A91280%5C%22%3Ehighlighted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%2099-year%20concession%20given%20in%20Tajpur%20port%20development%20was%20the%20first%20instance%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Adanis%20hurriedly%20pulling%20out%20of%20such%20a%20project%20out%20of%20a%20political%20controversy%20does%20not%20make%20sense%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20journalist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20bagged%20the%20LoI%20after%20emerging%20as%20the%20highest%20bidder%2C%20defeating%20another%20major%20business%20group%2C%20JSW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20bureaucrat%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%2C%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20was%20%E2%80%9Cshocking%20and%20surprising%E2%80%9D%20as%20there%20was%20no%20hint%20of%20such%20a%20measure%20even%20a%20day%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20chief%20minister%20may%20have%20been%20upset%20that%20no%20one%20from%20the%20Adanis%20came%20to%20give%20updates%20on%20the%20project.%20But%20I%20totally%20understand%20if%20the%20Adanis%20did%20not%20send%20any%20representative%20to%20avoid%20being%20asked%20by%20the%20press%20on%20the%20Mahua%20Moitra%20episode%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bureaucrat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20Avijit%20Ghosal%2C%20however%2C%20suspects%20the%20chief%20minister%20may%20have%20miscommunicated%20what%20she%20intended%20to%20convey%20on%20November%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMega%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20this%20do%20not%20happen%20overnight%20and%20the%20LoI%20is%20nearly%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20very%20long%20drawn%20process%20of%20negotiations%20and%20a%20string%20of%20agreements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20should%20have%20clarified%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20the%20chief%20minister%20may%20have%20meant%20is%20that%20while%20the%20Adanis%20remain%20the%20anchor%20investor%20in%20this%20project%2C%20there%20would%20be%20multiple%20sub-projects%20with%20wide%20investment%20opportunities%20for%20India%20Inc.%20She%20probably%20invited%20other%20industrial%20houses%20for%20wider%20investment.%20What%20she%20perhaps%20omitted%20was%20providing%20an%20explanation%20for%20her%20one-line%20statement.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20explanation%20that%20the%20state%20industries%20minister%20is%20providing%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghosal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20will%20invest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcommitted-to-tajpur-port-waiting-for-formalities-from-bengal-govt-adani-official%2Farticleshow%2F97844349.cms%5C%22%3ERs%2015%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20project%2C%20while%20the%20associated%20infrastructural%20development%20cost%20has%20been%20projected%20at%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uniindia.com%2F~%2Fadani-port-receives-loi-for-tajpur-from-mamata-govt%2FStates%2Fnews%2F2840789.html%5C%22%3ERs%2010%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20November%2021%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20mentioned%20Tajpur%20as%20a%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701089107000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04121914%2FF6AYMqwXkAAlspp.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fadani-group-tajpur-port-bengal-government-u-turn-mystery%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20days%20after%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20fresh%20investment%20call%2C%20industries%20minister%20Shashi%20Panka%20said%20discussions%20with%20Adani%20are%20continuing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fadani-group-tajpur-port-bengal-government-u-turn-mystery%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chris%20Evans'%20wife%20Alba%20flaunts%20wedding%20ring%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701089086000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105537328%2Cimgsize-39512.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fchris-evans-wife-alba-baptista-flaunts-wedding-ring-for-first-time-since-secret-nuptials-see-photo%2Farticleshow%2F105537328.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105537328.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlba%20Baptista%2C%20star%20of%20'Warrior%20Nun'%2C%20was%20seen%20wearing%20a%20sparkli