%3EThe%20news%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20highest%20number%20of%20employees%20%E2%80%93%20101%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20terminated%20in%20Siang%20district%2C%20followed%20by%2072%20in%20Changlang%C2%A0%20(district)%20and%2026%20in%20Anjaw%20(district).%E2%80%9D%20It%20said%20they%20were%20appointed%20to%20these%20posts%20between%202018%20and%20early%20this%20year%20by%20the%20state%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECalling%20it%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20biggest%20en-mass%20termination%20letters%20issued%20by%20any%20department%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20administration%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2023%2F11%2F24%2Fedn-dept-issues-termination-letters-to-255-illegal-appointees%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EArunachal%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20they%20were%20appointed%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20Staff%20Selection%20Board%20Recruitment%20Rules%2C%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EState%20education%20commissioner%20Amjad%20Kak%20told%20reporters%20in%20Itanagar%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20did%20scrutiny%20at%20the%20departmental%20level%2C%20issued%20show%20cause%20notices%20to%20all%2C%20and%20the%20termination%20orders%20were%20issued%20after%20the%20lapse%20of%20the%20notice%20period.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20controversial%20issue%20was%20first%20raised%20in%20March%202021%20by%20former%20Congress%20MP%20Ninong%20Ering.%20In%20response%2C%20though%20the%20chief%20minister%20Khandu%20had%20said%20strict%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20if%20the%20accusation%20was%20found%20to%20be%20true%2C%20but%20nothing%20much%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20caught%20the%20public%20eye%20though.%20This%20past%20May%2C%20a%20student%20body%20accused%20the%20education%20department%20of%20appointing%2028%20primary%20school%20teachers