ressive%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20Congress%2C%20the%20grand%20old%20party%2C%20was%20written%20off.%20Crestfallen%20party%20leaders%20and%20cadres%20were%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20alternative%20options%20for%20their%20political%20survival.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20anyone%20in%20Telangana%20would%20agree%20(barring%20the%20ruling%20BRS)%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20stock%20has%20gone%20up%20by%20several%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20339px)%2085vw%2C%20339px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22339%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22280%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20contention%20about%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20ascendancy%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20question%2C%20however%2C%20is%20whether%20it%20has%20grown%20to%20the%20extent%20where%20it%20can%20wrest%20power.%20Even%20as%20we%20inch%20closer%20to%20the%20polling%20date%20(November%2030)%2C%20pollsters%20are%20still%20not%20able%20to%20call%20the%20election.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20discernible%20wave%20for%20or%20against%20the%20BRS%2C%20and%20likewise%20the%20Congress.%20This%20is%20evidenced%20by%20numerous%20surveys%2C%20each%20one%20of%20them%20projecting%20vastly%20different%20numbers%20for%20the%20two%20main%20contenders%2C%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20Congress.%20Some%20of%20them%20even%20don%E2%80%99t%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20hung%20assembly%2C%20with%20some%20giving%20the%20BRS%20a%20slight%20edge%20and%20others%20for%20the%20Congress.%20One%20thing%20common%20in%20these%20surveys%20is%20the%20clear%20resurgence%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20could%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20upturn%3A%20Perceived%20anti-incumbency%20at%20the%20constituency%20level%20against%20BRS%20MLAs%3B%20energy%20infused%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20in%20the%20party%20leaders%20and%20cadres%3B%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decline%20following%20the%20removal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-cracks-appearing-in-bjps-telangana-unit-after-the-karnataka-debacle%5C%22%3EBandi%20Sanjay%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20Telangana%20unit%20chief%3B%20and%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20BRS%20and%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20are%20in%20cahoots%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMessaging%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20sole%20credit%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20establishment%20of%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BRS%20describe%20themselves%20as%20%3Cem%3Eichchina%3C%2Fem%3E%20party%20(the%20party%20that%20granted%20the%20statehood)%20and%20%3Cem%3Etechchina%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eparty%20(the%20party%20that%20achieved%20statehood%20through%20agitation)%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20training%20its%20guns%20on%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20and%20his%20family%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20turning%20Telangana%20into%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfiefdom%E2%80%9D%2C%20much%20like%20the%20feudal%20lords%20(Doras)%20of%20the%20yore.%20The%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20appears%20to%20have%20found%20some%20takers%2C%20given%20the%20widespread%20allegations%20against%20KCR%20that%20he%20is%20inaccessible%20(which%20earned%20him%20the%20moniker%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfarmhouse%20CM%E2%80%9D)%20and%20that%20power%20is%20concentrated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204101%2Fkcr-ktr.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204101%2Fkcr-ktr.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204101%2Fkcr-ktr-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204101%2Fkcr-ktr-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-425083%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EK.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20with%20his%20son%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20foregrounded%20alleged%20repression%20under%20KCR%2C%20that%20he%20had%20engineered%20defections%20of%20opposition%20MLAs%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20curb%20political%20dissent%20as%20well%20as%20numerous%20instances%20of%20the%20arrest%20of%20civil%20society%20members%20and%20closure%20of%20civil%20society%20spaces.%20The%20widespread%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20KCR%20and%20his%20family%20members%2C%20including%20in%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20much-publicised%20Kaleshwaram%20Project%2C%20have%20also%20provided%20fodder%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%2C%20which%20has%20been%20egging%20on%20the%20people%20to%20join%20hands%20in%20%E2%80%9Canother%20struggle%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cliberate%E2%80%9D%20Telangana%20from%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDorala%20Palana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(rule%20by%20Doras)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-brs-anti-incumbency-congress%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Polls%3A%20Can%20BRS%20Fend%20Off%20Anti-Incumbency%20Sentiment%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManifesto%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20lines%20of%20its%20Karnataka%20manifesto%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20announced%20six%20%E2%80%98guarantees%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20voters%20of%20Telangana.%20The%20manifesto%2C%20which%20is%20high%20on%20welfare%20and%20covers%20various%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20could%20work%20in%20its%20favour.%20The%20BRS%2C%20aware%20of%20the%20damage%20potential%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fbrs-attempts-to-trump-congress-manifesto-with-few-more-novel-sops%2Farticle67424024.ece%5C%22%3Esought%20to%20outshine%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20its%20own%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20Mahalaxmi%20guarantee%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20announced%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%20to%20eligible%20women.%20The%20BRS%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20promises%20Rs%203%2C000%20as%20a%20monthly%20honorarium.%20While%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%20an%20LPG%20cylinder%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20the%20BRS%20has%20said%20it%20will%20offer%20the%20same%20at%20Rs%20400.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20increase%20investment%20support%20given%20to%20farmers%20(under%20the%20existing%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20of%20the%20BRS%20government)%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20acre%20per%20year.%20The%20Congress%20has%20also%20gone%20a%20step%20further%20by%20promising%20it%20to%20tenant%20farmers%20as%20well%2C%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20benefit%20under%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme.%20The%20BRS%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20promised%20to%20make%20it%20Rs%2016%2C000%20per%20acre%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20its%20Cheyutha%20scheme%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20Rs%204%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20old-age%20pension%20beneficiaries.%20The%20BRS%20has%20assured%20them%20that%20it%20would%20raise%20the%20amount%20from%20existing%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20largely%20banking%20on%20the%20youth%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Ftelanganas-exam-hub-trials-and-tribulations-of-job-aspirants-9033684%2F%5C%22%3Egovernment%20job%20aspirants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20are%20angry%20with%20the%20BRS%20government.%20Even%20by%20its%20own%20admission%2C%20the%20BRS%20government%20has%20failed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fthe-unemployment-problem-in-telangana-what-jobs-data-tells-us%5C%22%3Eunemployed%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state%2C%20by%20not%20being%20able%20to%20fill%20vacancies%20and%20conduct%20recruitment%20exams%20without%20any%20irregularities.%20The%20youth%20seems%20clearly%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BRS%2C%20which%20could%20help%20shore%20up%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20gone%20even%20a%20step%20further%20by%20announcing%20a%20job%20calendar%2C%20confident%20of%20forming%20the%20next%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20segments%20who%20are%20disillusioned%20by%20the%20BRS%20government%20are%20government%20employees%20who%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20long%20for%20interim%20relief%2C%20restoration%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%2C%20and%20Pay%20Revision%20Commission%20(PRC)%2C%20among%20other%20issues.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20those%20who%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F260923%2Fdalit-bc-bandhu-gruha-lakshmi-fear-brs-mlas.html%5C%22%3Eleft%20out%20of%20the%20BRS%20government%20schemes%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Dalit%20Bandhu%20and%20double-bedroom%20housing%20could%20potentially%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Both%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20minorities%20could%20also%20rally%20behind%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20its%20effective%20messaging%20that%20the%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20are%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20BRS%20has%20lowered%20significantly%20since%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20party%20could%20play%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-bjp-isnt-a-frontrunner-but-could-it-be-a-spoilsport%5C%22%3Espoilsport%20for%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20splitting%20the%20anti-incumbency%20votes%20in%20several%20constituencies.%20The%20Congress%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20a%20stiff%20fight%20for%20anti-BRS%20votes%20in%20about%2020%20seats%2C%20including%20in%20Korutla%2C%20LB%20Nagar%2C%20Bodhan%2C%20Kamareddy%2C%20Nirmal%2C%20Maheshwaram%2C%20and%20in%20a%20few%20handful%20of%20seats%20of%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Congress%2C%20it%20is%20still%20an%20uphill%20task%20despite%20the%20positive%20perception%20it%20has%20built%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%20given%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20role%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20public%20relations%20overdrive%20and%20poll%20management.%20A%20senior%20party%20leader%20remarked%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government%20in%20the%20state%20even%20if%20it%20wins%20one%20seat%20less%20than%2060%20in%20the%20119-member%20assembly%20due%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20coming%20together.%20Can%20the%20Congress%20pull%20off%20a%20handsome%20victory%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701077347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fresu