gns%20that%20the%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20putting%20in%20more%20effort%20to%20stop%20the%20Congress%20from%20possibly%20riding%20on%20what%20many%20see%20as%20a%20massive%20eleventh-hour%20momentum%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20399px)%2085vw%2C%20399px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22329%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20last%20week%20before%20the%20polls%20has%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fif-bjp-brs-were-not-friends-ed-and-cbi-would-have-been-after-kcr-says-rahul-gandhi%2Farticle67577452.ece%5C%22%3Etargeted%20raids%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20now%20openly%20seen%20as%20an%20unabashed%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20on%20prominent%20Congress%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20G.%20Vivek%2C%20was%20in%20the%20BJP%20until%20very%20recently%20and%20switched%20to%20the%20Congress%20on%20November%201%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20electioneering.%20Vivek%20was%20also%20head%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%C2%A0%20manifesto%20committee%20until%20he%20deserted%20the%20BJP%20last%20month.%20Probably%20like%20many%20others%20he%20too%C2%A0%20saw%20the%20late%20surge%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Vivek%20c