ashekhar%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fresurgent-congress-telangana-brs%5C%22%3E%20Can%20the%20Resurgent%20Congress%20Wrest%20Telangana%20from%20the%20BRS%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20possibly%20read%20this%20sentiment%20early%20on.%20A%20local%20BJP%20leader%20who%20had%20left%20BRS%20to%20join%20the%20party%20last%20year%20told%20this%20writer%20that%20the%20state%20party%20cadres%20were%20puzzled%20when%20just%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20chose%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funion-minister-kishan-reddy-made-telangana-bjp-chief-punjab-jharkhand-get-new-presidents%5C%22%3Ereplace%20the%20dynamic%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20with%20G.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20as%20party%20organisation%20chief%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBandi%2C%20a%20popular%20BJP%20leader%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20from%20Karimnagar%2C%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20favourite%20of%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20his%20removal%20in%20early%20July%20raised%20many%20eyebrows%20among%20the%20BJP%20cadres.%20He%20also%20told%20me%20that%20the%20local%20BJP%20leadership%20wanted%20to%20launch%20a%20massive%20campaign%20around%20corruption%20cases%20involving%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20or%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20family%20but%20it%20received%C2%A0%20lukewarm%20response%20from%20the%20central%20leadership%20of%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20BJP%20leadership%20wanted%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20Kavitha%2C%20to%20be%20arrested%20by%20ED%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20excise%20case%20but%20the%20Centre%20did%20not%20oblige%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20created%20immense%20confusion%20within%20the%20BJP%20cadres%2C%20said%20the%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20son%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20(KTR)%2C%20dismisses%20this%20theory%20as%20unfounded%20and%20told%20a%20visiting%20group%20of%20journalists%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Kavitha%20not%20being%20arrested%20by%20ED%20is%20seen%20as%20evidence%20of%20a%20deal%20between%20BJP%20and%20BRS%20then%20you%20should%20also%20see%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20or%20Rahul%20not%20being%20arrested%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHerald%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%20as%20a%20deal%20between%20Congress%20and%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKTR%20is%20confident%20that%20his%20party%20will%20win%20a%20third%20term%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20massive%20welfare%20provided%20to%20farmers%2C%20womenfolk%20and%20the%20poor%20in%20general.%20%E2%80%9COur%20record%20is%20there%20for%20all%20to%20see.%20We%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20highest%20per%20capita%20income%20state%20in%20the%20country%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20Our%20per%20capita%20spending%20on%20welfare%20is%20also%20among%20the%20highest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKTR%20admits%20there%20is%20some%20anti-incumbency%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20is%20natural%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20admits%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20improving%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20from%20a%20very%20low%20base%20and%20the%20gap%20between%20BRS%20and%20Congress%20is%20too%20large%20to%20cover%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20thing%20KTR%20is%20certain%20about.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20reduced%20BJP%20to%20nothing%20and%20we%20have%20proved%20their%20primordial%20identity%C2%A0%20politics%20will%20only%20work%20in%20the%20cow%20belt%20of%20North%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20recent%20years%20had%20tried%20everything%20to%20choke%20Telangana%20finances%20to%20disrupt%20infrastructure%20spending%20and%20welfare%20delivery.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Centre%20has%20virtually%20imposed%20economic%20sanctions%20on%20us%20like%20it%20is%20done%20internationally%20against%20enemy%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20KTR%20also%20said%20the%20central%20BJP%20leaders%20campaigning%20in%20Telangana%20are%20actually%20doing%20so%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20have%20no%20expectations%20from%20the%20current%20state%20elections.%20This%20assertion%20of%20KTR%E2%80%99s%20provides%20a%20clue%20to%20a%20possible%20shift%20in%20the%20Modi-Shah%20strategy%20for%20South%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20for%20the%20next%20six%20months%20or%20so%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20for%20much%20of%20South%20India%20is%20to%20build%20some%20level%20of%20understanding%20with%20the%20regional%20parties%20so%20that%20their%20support%20could%20be%20sought%20in%20the%20event%20it%20falls%20short%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20creative%20abuse%20of%20the%20ED%20is%20very%20much%20part%20of%20building%20such%20understanding%20with%20regional%20parties%20in%20South%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20also%20explain%20why%20the%20BJP%20is%20making%20every%20last%20minute%20effort%20to%20choke%20the%20Congress%20numbers%20in%20Telangana%20and%20in%20turn%20enabling%20the%20BRS%20get%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20visible%20surge%20in%20support%20for%20the%20Congress%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20it%20would%20cover%20the%20massive%20existing%20gap%20with%20BRS.%20The%20Congress%20vote%20share%20of%2029%25%20is%20way%20lower%20than%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20(then%20TRS)%2047%25%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections.%20BRS%20had%2088%20seats%20against%20Congress%E2%80%99s%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20there%20a%20big%20enough%20wave%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20reach%20the%20halfway%20mark%20of%2060%20seats%3F%20This%20is%20really%20the%20key%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20activist%20and%20former%20psephologist%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20says%20there%20is%20not%20just%20a%20wave%20but%20a%20gathering%20storm%20or%20%3Cem%3Eaandhi%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Yadav%20had%20stuck%20his%20neck%20out%20in%20Karnataka%20against%20all%20other%20prognoses%20and%20given%20the%20Congress%20a%20big%20lead.%20He%20was%20proved%20right.%20If%20he%20is%20proved%20right%20again%20then%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20central%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20calculations%20could%20go%20awry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701076846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27142040%2FUntitled-design-7-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-brs-and-the-truth-behind-the-conspiracy-theories%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Is%20the%20BJP%20putting%20in%20more%20effort%20to%20stop%20the%20Congress%20from%20possibly%20riding%20on%20what%20many%20see%20as%20a%20massive%20eleventh-hour%20momentum%20in%20its%20favour%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-brs-and-the-truth-behind-the-conspiracy-theories%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Audi%20India%20raises%20prices%20of%20vehicles%20by%202%25%20from%20Jan%201%20on%20rising%20input%20costs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701076476000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2018-01%2F18%2Ffull%2F1516274257-8585.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faudi-india-raises-prices-of-vehicles-by-2-from-jan-1-on-rising-input-costs-123112700465_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Audi%20India%20registered%20an%2088%20per%20cent%20growth%20and%20has%20retailed%205%2C530%20units%20in%20the%20first%20nine%20months%20of%20this%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faudi-india-raises-prices-of-vehicles-by-2-from-jan-1-on-rising-input-costs-123112700465_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompani