ovember%2023%20to%20November%2025%20after%20receiving%20representations%20that%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20scale%20wedding%E2%80%9D%20ceremonies%20were%20scheduled%20on%20the%20earlier%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20the%20Mizoram%20Kohhran%20Hruaitute%20Committee%20(MKHC)%2C%20a%20conglomerate%20of%2015%20major%20churches%20of%20the%20state%2C%20urged%20all%20churches%20this%20past%20Saturday%20(November%2025)%20to%20organise%20prayers%20during%20the%20Sunday%20church%20service%20to%20seek%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20from%20God%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20change%20in%20the%20counting%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%20Presbyterian%20Church%2C%20the%20largest%20denomination%20in%20the%20state%2C%20also%20separately%20urged%20its%20members%20to%20hold%20prayers%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20date%20of%20counting%20is%20changed%2C%20said%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.themizorampost.net%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMizoram%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20five-member%20delegation%20of%20the%20NGO%20Coordination%20Committee%20(NGOCC)%2C%20an%20Aizawl-based%20umbrella%20body%20of%20NGOs%20and%20student%20organisations%2C%20has%20been%20staying%20put%20in%20New%20Delhi%20since%20the%20past%20week%20to%20seek%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20(CEC)%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20delegation%20has%20come%20to%20the%20national%20Capital%20after%20pleas%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20political%20parties%20to%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC)%20went%20unheard.%20Those%20pleas%20were%20made%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20CEC%20in%20New%20Delhi%20had%20announced%20the%20election%20schedule%20in%20the%20state%20along%20with%20December%203%20as%20the%20common%20date%20for%20counting%20of%20votes%20in%20all%20the%20five%20poll-bound%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENews%20reports%20said%20the%20CEC%