istoric-witch-bottles-in-the-gulf%2Famp_articleshow%2F105530002.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IFFI%20Daily%E2%80%99s%20Refusal%20to%20Print%20Konkani%20Poem%20on%20Caste%20Discrimination%20Draws%20Criticism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fvishnu.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20International%20Film%20Festival%20of%20India%20(IFFI)%20was%20mired%20in%20controversy%20after%20its%20daily%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Peacock%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20decided%20not%20to%20print%20the%20translation%20of%20a%20Konkani%20poem%20on%20caste%20discrimination%20written%20by%20late%20Goan%20writer%20and%20former%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MLA%20from%20St%20Andre%2C%20Vishnu%20Surya%20Wagh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sunday%20edition%20of%20the%20daily%20featured%20a%20two-page%20illustration%20of%20Wagh%20by%20artist%20Siddhesh%20Gautam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fiffi-censorship-row-vishnu-surya-wagh-poem-on-caste-discrimination-triggers-controversy-siddhesh-gautam-9043736%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20illustration%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20carried%20alongside%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20poem%20%E2%80%98Secular%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20text%20was%20removed%20on%20Saturday%20(November%2025).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poem%20is%20republished%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20nephew%2C%20Kaustubh%20Naik%2C%20called%20it%20an%20%E2%80%9Cact%20of%20censorship%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaik%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Peacock%3C%2Fem%3E%20team%20had%20asked%20him%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20to%20translate%20the%20poem%20from%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20collection%20titled%20%E2%80%98Sudirsukta%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20wanted%20me%20to%20vet%20some%20poems.%20I%20asked%20them%20if%20they%20had%20any%20specific%20poem%20in%20mind%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20translate%20this%20particular%20one.%20The%20poem%20was%20to%20accompany%20a%20double-page%20spread%20illustration%20on%20Wagh%20by%20the%20anti-caste%20artist%20Siddhesh%20Gautam%20in%20the%20Sunday%20edition%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Peacock%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Entertainment%20Society%20of%20Goa%20(ESG)%20officials%20informed%20him%20that%20the%20poem%20would%20not%20be%20included%20in%20the%20print.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20poem%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Canti-establishment%20stance%E2%80%9D%20and%20themes%20could%20be%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20to%20not%20print%20the%20poem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20poetry%20collection%20Sudirsukta%20caused%20some%20controversy%20in%202017%20%E2%80%A6%20If%20you%20read%20the%20collection%2C%20you%20realise%20that%20Wagh%20recorded%20histories%20of%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20through%20his%20poems.%20The%20use%20of%20language%20and%20its%20imagery%20and%20themes%20are%20rather%20revolutionary%20in%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20literary%20scene.%20The%20poems%20take%20an%20anti-establishment%20stance.%20Perhaps%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20this%20act%20of%20censorship%20occurred%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20Constitution%20day%20%5BNovember%2025%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20anthology%20of%20poems%20in%20Konkani%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Sudirsukta%20%E2%80%93%20Hymns%20of%20a%20Shudra%2C%E2%80%99%20got%20the%20Goa%20Konkani%20Academy%20Award%20in%20the%20poetry%20category.%20However%2C%20controversy%20ensued%20when%20news%20of%20the%20award%20%E2%80%9Cleaked%20before%20the%20official%20announcement%2C%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20allegations%20that%20the%20book%20endorsed%20communal%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fgoa-poet-first-awarded-hounded-police-questioning-brahmins%5C%22%3Ewas%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20social%20media%20campaign%20lifted%20its%20verses%20and%20shared%20them%20%E2%80%9Cout%20of%20context%E2%80%9D%2C%20triggering%20a%20caste%20divide%20between%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20dominant%20Gaud%20Saraswat%20Brahmins%20(GSB)%20and%20the%20majority%20Bahujan%20Goans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20awards%20for%20that%20year%20were%20cancelled%20by%20the%20then-chief%20minister%2C%20the%20late%20Manohar%20Parrikar%2C%20who%20incidentally%20belonged%20to%20the%20GSB%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20also%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%2C%20saying%2C%20on%20Instagram%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20asked%20to%20not%20publish%20a%20poem%20by%20Vishnu%20Surya%20Wagh%20for%20today%E2%80%99s%20issue.%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20poem%20%E2%80%98Secular%E2%80%99%20(is%20one%20that)%20I%20carefully%20chose%20because%20it%20expresses%20so%20many%20incidents%20of%20caste%20discrimination%20by%20many%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20in%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas.%20I%20myself%20have%20gone%20through%20something%20similar%20many%20times%20in%20my%20life%2C%20not%20just%20as%20an%20unknown%20student%2C%20but%20also%20as%20a%20well-known%20artist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ESG%20is%20the%20nodal%20agency%20that%20organises%20IFFI%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Goa%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20include%20the%20poem%20was%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cpurely%20for%20creative%20reasons%E2%80%9D.%20ESG%20is%20also%20the%20publisher%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Peacock%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EESG%20CEO%20Ankita%20Mishra%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20decision%20to%20not%20print%20the%20article%20was%20an%20editorial%20call%20taken%20purely%20for%20creative%20reasons%20and%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20content%20of%20the%20article.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C(The)%20%3Cem%3EPeacock%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20been%20a%20flagbearer%20for%20artistic%20freedom%20since%20its%20inception%2C%20and%20it%20is%20our%20endeavour%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC0GOnRQSNkl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26ig_rid%3D9e9cfe10-95c1-4bcb-b45d-17efd77f0c4c%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESecular%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(By%20Vishnu%20Surya%20Wagh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20by%20Kaustubh%20Naik)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20was%20unaware%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EOf%20their%20technique%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ETo%20sniff%20people%E2%80%99s%20caste%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOne%20day%2C%20visiting%20a%20friend%E2%80%99s%20house%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EEncountered%20his%20uncle%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ELounging%20on%20the%20balc%C3%A3o%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EAnd%20we%20began%20conversing%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWagh%3F%20You%E2%80%99re%20one%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUncle%20smirked.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EI%20felt%20a%20pang%20of%20anxiety.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYet%2C%20he%20sought%20absolute%20certainty.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ESo%20he%20inquired%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kamat%20Waghs%20of%20Ribandar%2C%20kin%20to%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20replied.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHailing%20from%20Karwar%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20from%20Goa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIndeed%3F%20Which%20part%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20Dongri%3F%20Perhaps%20the%20Mahajans%20of%20the%20Rama%20temple%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNo.%20Our%20goddess%20is%20Sati.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EStill%20unable%20to%20deduce%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EHe%20probed%20once%20more.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20your%20family%20deity%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CShivnath%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20offered.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20Shiroda%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CYes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSo%E2%80%A6so%20you%20are%20not%20a%20GSB.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20uncle%2C%20we%20are%20Bhandaris.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20chuckle%20escaped%20him.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20take%20offense!%20I%20asked%20out%20of%20curiosity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EWe%20renounce%20caste.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ECome%2C%20have%20tea.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ECaste%20systems%20have%20marred%20Goa.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EWho%20is%20Baman%3F%20Who%20is%20Shudra%3F%20Who%20cares%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EThese%20divisions%20hold%20no%20meaning.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EWe%20should%20be%20secular.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EWe%20must%20have%20a%20casteless%20society%2C%20you%20know%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUncle%20waited%2C%20anticipation%20in%20the%20air%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20merely%20nodded%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESipping%20tea%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20gaze%2C%20firm%20on%20his%20sacred%20thread%E2%80%99s%20descent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701071731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fvishnu.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fiffl-dailys-refusal-to-print-konkani-poem-on-caste-discrimination-draws