les%20that%20are%20made%20from%20agricultural%20produce%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrothers%20Suresh%20and%20Prafful%20Sanghavi%20were%20working%20in%20the%20field%20during%20the%20peak%20of%20World%20War%20II.%20Seeing%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20soldiers%2C%20they%20would%20prepare%20lemon%20syrups%20and%20juices%20from%20the%20produce%20on%20their%20land%20and%20serve%20these%20to%20the%20army.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20soon%20began%20to%20realise%20the%20potential%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263689%2Findia-nilons-pickles-iconic-brands-suresh-prafful-sanghavi-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20processing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Soon%2C%20their%20home%20kitchen%20in%20Utran%20village%2C%20Jalgaon%2C%20Maharashtra%20became%20a%20site%20of%20experimentation.%20Aromas%20of%20ketchup%2C%20jellies%2C%20jams%20and%20more%20prepared%20with%20ingredients%20sourced%20from%20the%20field%20began%20to%20fill%20the%20space.%20However%2C%20when%20sold%2C%20these%20did%20not%20generate%20a%20good%20response%20from%20the%20audience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201966%2C%20the%20brothers%20introduced%20pickles%20to%20the%20menu%20and%20sales%20rocketed!%20That%20is%20how%20Nilon%20pickles%20was%20born.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Chitale%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FChitale_11zon-1700660560.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bakarwadi%20at%20Chitale%20is%20famous%20and%20thousands%20of%20kgs%20are%20prepared%20everyday%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2